Process - STEPS
In Git make sure you are in master brach
PULL to get latest version of master
Create a new branch for the work you are about to do. Give the branch a name jazz_api, jazz_sql
Make sure you are in your branch
Make changes
Commit and push on your branch
Make pull request
Merge to Master if you are sure it will not break anything
Otherwise request review













